# Variable Types Reference

Tera templates support several variable types.

## Scalar Types

- **string**: Text values (e.g., "hello")
- **boolean**: True or false values
- **number**: Numeric values (integers or floats)

## Collection Types

- **array**: List of items
- **object**: Key-value pairs

## Usage in Templates

```tera
{{ string_variable }}
{% if boolean_variable %}content{% endif %}
{% for item in array_variable %}{{ item }}{% endfor %}
{{ object_variable.key }}
```
